{"type":"message","id":"d7c224ba","parentId":"5eb84983","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:46:22.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提到了两个问题：\n\n1. \"我要怎么配置能让你和其他的 机器人 agent 进行沟通\" - 如何配置我与其他机器人agent进行沟通\n2. \"hello\" - 打招呼\n\n看起来用户可能想了解如何让不同的AI agent之间进行协作或通信。让我先检查一下可用的agents和配置。\n\n让我先回复问候，然后解答关于agent沟通的问题。我需要查看：\n1. agents_list - 查看可用的agents\n2. sessions_list - 查看当前的sessions\n\n让我先检查一下可用的agents。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋\n\n关于你之前问的如何让我和其他机器人 agent 进行沟通，让我先查看一下当前可用的 agents 配置。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_GpPRYoHBRZIpC5w8DvyF4PHx","name":"agents_list","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":7797,"output":142,"cacheRead":7936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15875,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774014374046}}
